{"type": "article", "id": 19479, "title": "圣诞节的巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-22T07:40:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135556r6UTWYGMRkwZKEBe.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组巧克力的包装上都画有卡通娃娃伸长手臂拥抱巧克力的图案，有活泼的童趣，暗示路过的人从货架上拿下来。四种包装上的人物可以想象成一个家庭，包括父母和两个女儿。背景搭配红、黄、蓝、紫四种颜色，营造温暖的节日气氛。适合即将到来的圣诞节互赠礼物。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150001toAMZLnO7hIqfC0z.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150002E1BiKHZDdu0NWg9P.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"563\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5212963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261500040YTBa9xGH6Nnkv2E.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"542\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150004JxVOk7tu8XP0gpfU.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150004TSxglmu5vFi4zVoC.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"558\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.51666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}